info.tip: Get some information about the bot, and some useful links.

serverinfo.tip: Get some information about the current server.

help.tip: View the categories, descriptions, and aliases of all available commands.

simonsays.tip: Get a response from the bot, repeating exactly what was said.

ping.tip: Get the ms timing it took the bot to process your ping.

botinvite.tip: Receive an invite link for the bot.

hug.tip: Tag a user and give them a hug!

nuzzle.tip: Tag a user and boop/nuzzle them!

ship.tip: Tag a user and see your compatability!

loveme.tip: Get some fuzzy lovin' from PrototonBot!

coinflip.tip: Flip a coin and get heads or tails!

punish.tip: Punish a user for being bad, or put your own reason!

lewdpunish.tip: Punish a user for being lewd!

yeet.tip: Yeet a user outta here like an empty soda can!

lick.tip: Tag a user and give them a friendly lick!

gamble.tip: Bet Protobucks and get either 0x to 3.75x your bet back!

sass.tip: hAvE ThE BoT RePeAt yOuR MeSsAgE WiTh sAsS!

profile.tip: View your profile/card, or somebody else's.

wallet.tip: View your profile/card in a very simple form.

inventory.tip: View what items you currently have in your inventory.

daily.tip: Earn some extra Protobucks once per day!

pat.tip: Give a user a pat once per day!

setprofile.tip: Sets the description on your profile. (240 char limit)

leaderboard.tip: View the top 15 users for Protobucks or Levels.

partnerup.tip: Set your partner. Mutuals get 5% boosted Chat XP and Protobucks.

settheme.tip: Set your profile theme to one that you own.

store.tip: View roles, effects, and items available for purchase!

upgrade.tip: Use your coins to upgrade stats.

buy.tip: Purchase items listed from the store.

chopdown.tip: Use an axe to get forestry items.

mine.tip: Use a pickaxe to get mineral items.

salvage.tip: Use a wrench to get mechanical items.

hope.tip: Get a hopeful sprite from the Danganronpa 1 Cast.

despair.tip: Get a despairful sprite from the Danganronpa 1 Cast.

hope2.tip: Get a hopeful sprite from the Danganronpa 2 Cast.

despair2.tip: Get a despairful sprite from the Danganronpa 2 Cast.

yasqueen.tip: Get a random image of Junko Enoshima.

kamakura.tip: Get a GIF related to Izuru Kamakura.

8ball.tip: Get a random response to your question from an 8 ball.

mood.tip: Get a response with a random mood and emoji.

roll.tip: Roll a tabletop themed die of your choice.

murdering.tip: Get a scenario of the Wulfonronpa Series Cast.

murdering-rp.tip: Get a scenario of the Wulfonronpa RP Cast.

murdering-all.tip: Get a scenario of both casts listed above combined.

enable.tip: Tag a channel (or none for the current) to enable commands for users.

disable.tip: Tag a channel (or none for the current) to disable commands for users.

logchannel.tip: Tag a channel (or none for the current) to set the log channel for the bot.

prefix.tip: Change the server's prefix for commands.

privacy.tip: Choose whether or not your server is considered public or private. (Features TBA)

levelups.tip: Enable or Disable Level-Up Messages for this server.

togglewelcomes.tip: Enable or Disable Weclome Messages for this server.

welcomechannel.tip: Tag a channel (or none for the current) to set the welcome channel for the bot.

massrolecheck.tip: Get a list of the top 15 users in your server with the most roles.

purge.tip: Purge 1 up to 100 messages in a channel.
